title: DDFP 118: Terence Newman, New Year's traditions
itunes:title: DDFP 118: Terence Newman, New Year's traditions
description:
Shek & Rank talk playoffs with Cincinnati Bengals defensive back Terence Newman and throw an NFL.com party in Studio 66, welcoming in Handsome Hank and ATL writers Marc Sessler and Dan Hanzus to chat about outdated New Year’s Eve traditions and the Wild Card games.
